{"tid":2173016,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[廣東人做...]中國遊戲陪練變陪瞓，388元操作20分鐘","createTime":"2020-08-25T03:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T06:29:14.000Z","uid":27240,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5be484ded1756ba9c5326ce25f7d154a484f64c","tid":2173016,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0976580567890657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F0976580567890657.jpg&h=6cad65bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，有消息指出中國比心陪練平台出現低俗內容，一些女陪練主動向玩家兜售「視像裸聊和性服務」，這些服務被指嚴重涉黃，其中也明碼標價。隨後比心陪練平台就此事發出聲明，已採取賬號凍結、列入黑名單風控系統等措施。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/47564745754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F47564745754.jpg&h=1665b997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當遊戲的陪練服務已不再是純粹的陪玩，那麼對遊戲的主要人群大部分青少年的危害是可想而知的。首先，北京心理諮詢專家範經韌表示，八成的遊戲是針對14-22歲之間的青少年，陪玩行業出現或濃或淡的性意味，這對青少年心理健康帶來極為惡劣影響，對青少年而言是極大的誘惑，還會引發早戀早性行為等嚴重問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5225223424233-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F5225223424233-1.jpg&h=25833d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其次，明碼標價的視像裸聊188元/20分鐘，露臉價格388元/20分鐘等遊戲體驗服務，玩家還可以通過語音交流和指揮，驗證是否真人實時表演。不利於青少年養成良好的消費習慣，更容易導致他們形成大手大腳的消費意識，這對他們本身來說是百害而無一利的。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/08/25/chinese-game-sparring-partner-to-become-a-sp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F08%2F25%2Fchinese-game-sparring-partner-to-become-a-sp%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXQ3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=abe46db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/08/25/chinese-game-sparring-partner-to-become-a-sp/</a>"},{"pid":"05ceb5f7e04bb3e341cb0164ffecd2ea59a5b9b3","tid":2173016,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"好過miss pun啲垃圾雞lin都唔露收幾嚿水<br />\n重要得相睇"},{"pid":"7bb9051ceb49424274196d81f1ed49658b2db783","tid":2173016,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"gchi陪瞓"},{"pid":"4ba941e29d4ba3d62ff3221c9dd0db8b0179d14b","tid":2173016,"uid":27240,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TO5C4xL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTO5C4xL.jpg&h=66951e17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72795dc754295aab46fc2138fdeb9bcd912f80ad","tid":2173016,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"證明廣東人平均時間只有20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27df98172d896b74e16cbadd5502902a23eefa2a","tid":2173016,"uid":129068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">不推文回覆</span>"},{"pid":"5cdf1f0172301166033d8cf514cfee2203a4f833","tid":2173016,"uid":105445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72795dc754295aab46fc2138fdeb9bcd912f80ad","tid":2173016,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"證明廣東人平均時間只有20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"日本飛田新地都係段分鐘計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715f1562737a559529e80ef613aa6309165cf46a","tid":2173016,"uid":70429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72795dc754295aab46fc2138fdeb9bcd912f80ad","tid":2173016,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"s